Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}eating{\i0} the Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's using brute force\Nto break free of our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We humans can no longer keep\Nthat Eva under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The awakening and liberation of Unit 01...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Seele won't take this lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eva series aren't meant to be able\Nto generate an S2 Drive on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted an Eva could\Nassimilate an S2 Drive in such manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This turn of events is in no way\Npart of Seele's scenario!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Compensating for this\Nwill be no small task.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps entrusting Nerv\Nto Gendoh Ikari, to that man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was a mistake in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it were not for that man, we could\Nnot have set any of our plans in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's begun, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It all starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage to the two Evas\Nis well beyond the Hayflick limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a while before things\Nget back to the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the Magi System\Nis designed to be transferable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start work as early as tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But this place is a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore they decide to condemn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have to make do with this, the\Nbackup Secondary Command Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without the Magi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll dust off the cobwebs\Nand get down to work this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairs are hard,\Nand the sensors aren't responsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be as productive\Nas we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This place's layout is identical to\Nour old First Command Center, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it feels {\i1}off{\i0} somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All that matters now\Nis that it's operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The big question\Nis whether or not Unit 01 is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will restraining it\Nusing the cage be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not detecting any thermal,\Nelectrical, EM,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or chemical energy readings\Nfrom inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The S2 Drive is completely inert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That hasn't stopped Unit 01 from\Ncoming to life three times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fiddle around with it\Nbased only on what we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what it might do to us\Nif we start poking at it blindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like {\i1}you,{\i0} Major Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 isn't our only problem, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Units 00 and 02\Nare severely damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv headquarters, partially destroyed.\NThe Central Dogma lies exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This damage is catastrophic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no telling how much time\Nand money this has cost us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened because there is\Nno bell around Ikari's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-We put one there. It just didn't ring.\N-A bell that doesn't ring is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll {\i1}make{\i0} the bell take action next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my. This is certainly\Nan unexpected development, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to explain this\Nto the Council? To Seele, rather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time,\NUnit 01 was not under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This was an unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, Unit 01 is grounded.\NUntil further orders from the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An appropriate response. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your son still absorbed into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck, ma'am. It's not accepting\Nthe plug ejection signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-The backup and simulated signals?\N-Also rejected, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct control circuits\Nwon't connect, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've patched into\Nthe plug's visual circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting it on the main screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What in... the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what a synchronization rate\Nof 400% looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!\NWhat the hell happened to Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been assimilated into Eva-01.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that even mean?\NWhat the hell are the Evas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They can only be described as objects\Nsimilar in shape to a human
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that was created by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Created by humans"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All you did was copy something\Nyou found in Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even try to claim they're originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not just a simple copy.\NThey've been given human will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're saying this is somebody's {\i1}will?{\i0}\N-Perhaps the Eva has--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix this, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You built the things, didn't you?!\NWhatever it takes, make this right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The government and Home Ministry{\i0}\N{\i1}both officially deny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}any involvement in the incident{\i0}\N{\i1}at the Spratly Islands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other news, today marks one month{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}since the Tokyo-2{\i0}\N{\i1}terrorist attack by a leftist,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the SSDF briefed the press{\i0}\N{\i1}on a mop-up operation to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, so she was alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to call\Nand bother me with that crap, Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't... I couldn't do\Na damn thing to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That Idiot Shinji upstaged me {\i1}again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A salvage operation to recover Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the lifeform that we call\N"Shinji" still exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that respect for human life I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing Shinji now is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just bet. It's not Shinji's life\Nthat Nerv is interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want to lose Unit 01 as a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We hypothesize that Shinji's body\Nhas lost its ego boundary delineation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's drifting in the entry plug\Nin a quantum state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that Shinji's\Nbeen transformed into a state
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can't detect visually?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The makeup of the LCL in the entry plug\Nhas undergone a chemical change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now very similar\Nto seawater on primitive Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The primordial soup, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All the matter that comprises Shinji\Nis still preserved within the plug,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and what can be called his soul\Nis also still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The proof is that his mental self-image\Nis manifesting a facsimile of his suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So by "salvage operation,"\Nwe mean reconstituting his body
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and affixing his psyche inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that even possible?\N-With the Magi's support, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Theoretically,{\i0} you mean.\NYou won't actually know until you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this? Where am I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An entry plug? Unit 01's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's nobody in it. {\i0}I'm{\i1} not in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are these people?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh. These are the people I know.{\i0}\N{\i1}The people who know me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I get it. This is everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that makes up my world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is supposed to be my world,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I'm not sure what this is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A projection from outside.{\i0}\N{\i1}A projection I don't like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, right! It's an enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our enemies! Things we call Angels{\i0}\N{\i1}that bear divine names.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Evas' target... Nerv's target!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The things that killed Misato's father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I fighting them?{\i0}\N{\i1}When it means going through this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those freaky things are attacking us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you're attacked,{\i0}\N{\i1}it's only natural to defend yourself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe we don't need a reason.{\i0}\N{\i1}Maybe I shouldn't think about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're all my enemies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anything that threatens me is an enemy!{\i0}\N{\i1}Anything that threatens us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right! What's wrong with{\i0}\N{\i1}defending yourself? Defending ourselves?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurt Tohji! You murdered Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hate your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}wouldn't{\i0} I hate a father like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I? I hardly ever see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is that why you hate him?\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want me! He abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I your substitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are! That has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cast aside because he has you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who decided to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all Father's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to Nerv that day\Nto tell him that I hated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you saying to get into this and have{\i0}\N{\i1}terrifying things happen to me, Father?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Correct.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to do that!\NWhat are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you left me\Nbecause you didn't need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I do now, so I sent for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's impossible for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for me, too. I've never seen\Nor heard of this thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I recognized the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I recognized this Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And on that day, I ran away!\NFrom Father and Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}LCL temperature holding steady at 38°C.{\i0}\N{\i1}Oxygen levels are green.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Radiated EM pulse function, nominal.{\i0}\N{\i1}Wave pattern is Bravo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All monitoring instrumentation{\i0}\N{\i1}is functioning normally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A salvage operation outline...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you could have put this together\Nin just one month, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could take the credit,\Nbut it's not my proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This data is from experiments\Nconducted ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like this happened before?\NDuring the Evas' development?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened before I joined Nerv.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother witnessed it firsthand,\Nbut I only know about it from our files.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened\Nwhen they tried the procedure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They failed, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So much kindness... It's so warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this what human warmth feels like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no idea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "lonely" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I never understood it before,\Nbut now I think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What does "happy" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I never understood it before,\Nbut now I think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they kind to you? Other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah.\N-Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm an Eva pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They take care of me{\i0}\N{\i1}because I pilot the Eva!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what lets me stay here.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's the only reason they put up with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-That's why I need to pilot the Eva.{\i0}\N{\i1}-And then what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And fight. Right, I need to fight{\i0}\N{\i1}the things they say are our enemies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, I can't lose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do as I'm told\Nand pilot the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do as I'm told and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That’s the only way... people will say...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Keep it up.{\i0}\N-{\i1}Do your best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing? Get your act together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kick some ass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep it up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well done, Shinji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Misato and Ms. Ritsuko and Asuka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Tohji and Kensuke and Father,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they all praise me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They praise me when I pilot the Eva!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They all tell me to pilot it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m going to impress Father.{\i0}\N{\i1}The Father that abandoned me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep it up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm trying! I'm trying my hardest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, somebody, be kind to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've fought so hard!{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm fighting as hard as I can!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So take care of me! Be kind to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I {\i0}am{\i1} kind to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji? Do you want to become one with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to become one, body and soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's something that feels{\i0}\N{\i1}really, really good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m ready, Shinji.{\i0}\N{\i1}I’m always ready for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Idiot Shinji. Do you want{\i0}\N{\i1}to become one with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to become one, body and soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's something that feels{\i0}\N{\i1}really, really good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is me who's asking, okay?{\i0}\N{\i1}So get your butt over here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji, do you want to become one with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to become one, body and soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's something that feels{\i0}\N{\i1}really, really good, Shinji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to become one with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you want to become one, body and soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's something that feels{\i0}\N{\i1}really, really good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, relax. Just let your heart go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All probes now inserted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}EM wave pattern has been fixed{\i0}\N{\i1}at zero minus three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Connection to ego boundary pulse complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Commence salvage procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that. Now sending signal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva is receiving signal.\NNo sign of rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceeding with transmission\Nof signals two and three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Subject cathexis shows normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No signs of destrudo detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Transfer subject to stage two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Sup, Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Idiot Shinji!{\i0}\N{\i1}-Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-'Sup, Shinji!{\i0}\N{\i1}-Hey, Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Shinji.{\i0}\N{\i1}-Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!\NHis ego boundary is trapped in a loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Try broadcasting the full waveform\Nspectrum in all directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not getting through. Our signals\Nare being trapped in Klein space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-What does that mean?\N-It means we failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort intervention. Reverse tangent graph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Return offset value to zero.\N-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Destrudo readings in primitive\Ncortical area! Pattern Sepia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Core pulse is also fluctuating!\NIt's gone to plus 0.3!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our top priority is maintaining\Nits current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-Prevent a backflow!\N-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus 0.5, 0.8... This is strange!\NI can't slow it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? {\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to come back, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva is rejecting signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The LCL's self-assembly is breaking down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure climbing inside plug!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort all operations! Cut the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!\NThe plug is beginning exit sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where am I?\N-{\i1}Inside the Eva.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside the Eva? I got into it again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't going to pilot the Eva anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promised myself that I wouldn't{\i0}\N{\i1}get into the Eva again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you did get into it.{\i0}\N{\i1}Into Evangelion Unit 01.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you're here right now\Nbecause you got into the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the person you are now\Nbecause you piloted the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reject that.\NThe fact that you piloted the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reject your past\Nor who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need to do is think hard\Nabout what you want to {\i1}become.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And choose for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of science\Nif it can't save one person?! Just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Shinji back! Give him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A smell? The smell of a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato? Ayanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know... It smells like Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will our baby have to grow up in{\i0}\N{\i1}the aftermath of the Second Impact?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this hell?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, as long as you have the will to live,{\i0}\N{\i1}you can turn anywhere into paradise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, you're alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Opportunities for happiness{\i0}\N{\i1}can be found everywhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, of course. You're right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you decided?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji if it's a boy. Rei if it's a girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji... Rei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Repairs on Unit 01 will be finished\Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the end, we humans will use\Neven the power of God as a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder. I heard the Council is\Nthinking about grounding Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion, the artificial human...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For something we created, don't you think\Nthey have way too many unknowns?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess the important thing\Nis that we managed to save Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do with it.\NI think that was all your doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's been a long time.\NWant to get a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sorry. I have plans tonight.\N-Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The instant she knows Shinji's safe,\Nshe runs off for a secret tryst...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'm not one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Ritsuko is looking down\Nher nose at me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,right about now, thinking I'm indecent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truer to the human condition\Nwhen you indulge in carnal desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The deception should hold for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Against who, Nerv Intelligence?\NOr Commander Ikari or Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Others," don't you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not all that interested in others,\Nbut you always feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}are{\i0} like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you still smoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Only after doing this.\NSo you're the only one who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, tell me... How far along is\Nthe Human Instrumentality Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If it can destroy humanity, why are\Nwe keeping Adam in our basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you hook up with me?\NYou want info on that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of it, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply honored to be exploited\Nby a fine lady such as yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't talk about that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I just want you\Nto know what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are Nerv\Nand Commander Ikari {\i1}really {\i0}after?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buster,\Nyou can't distract me by doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch what you're sticking in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're messing around {\i1}now? {\i0}What {\i1}is{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A present from me.\NThe first one in eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the last I ever give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deputy Cdr. Fuyutsuki{\i0}\N{\i1}is abducted by Seele,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and several past incidents cross his mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything began in Kyoto in 1999.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Nerv really be mankind's stronghold?{\i0}
